schemas.content:
type Billing {
  id: ID!
  price: Int
  stripeId: String
  plan: String
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  email: String!
  name: String!
  lastname: String!
  roles: [String!]!
  billing: Billing!
}

schemas.content:
type Listing {
  id: ID!
  name: String!
  category: String!
  description: String!
  price: Int!
  latitude: Float!
  longitude: Float!
  amenities: [String!]!
  pictureUrl: String
  owner: User!
}
type Query {
  findListings: [Listing!]!
}
